      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON ROCHELLE (1) is drawn well on the inside. Last start finished 7th over 300m at this track beaten 5 lengths (17.18) behind Be Gritty in a Grade 5 on July 17. Looks a leading chance and expected to go close. FRENZY (3) was out of placings last time (31.83) at The Meadows in a Grade 5, finishing seventh and beaten 23 lengths. Has already won two times from this draw. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. SUN IN CUBA (7) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 1.5 lengths (19.66) at this track. The form from her last run stacks up well. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. MAJOR ILLUSION (2) is worth including.",
